Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公他人呢?
