Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧.........
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一．起．来．吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.45,0:01:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自那天以来的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.99,0:01:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都还感觉得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.36,0:01:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管到哪里都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.27,0:01:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管做什么都好让人心动
