Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都好像魔法师一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以让人高兴起来
