Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.52,0:02:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“老公别死啊!!\N用认真的力量往前冲!”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轮到岩城同学了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，过来看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，不得了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦好啦，现在可是修学旅行\N可不是什么蜜月旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好讨厌喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.48,0:03:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~又抽到鬼了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.28,0:03:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么又抽到了啦!真是的...\N来，换元气同学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提不起劲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得少了什么耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少了什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不太清楚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我知道了\N菜搞老师 对吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的!你还不肯死心啊\N帮你叫一下吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜~搞~老...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.47,0:03:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多管闲事啦! 白~痴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是觉得有点...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.36,0:04:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公! 老公!\N老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...快醒来啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直都这样子没醒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.08,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然没有明显的外伤\N不过头部受到强烈撞击，昏了过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~ 看到海了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.51,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是...总觉得...\N以前也曾遇到过这种光景...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?我是为了什么要潜下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像曾在这里\N跟什么人说过话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公他...会怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经尽力了\N今晚会是生死关头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果过了今晚\N还是没醒过来的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家不要这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.78,0:05:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧的 友纪这孩子\N没那么容易就倒下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啦\N他很快就会好起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啧，怎么大家都睡着了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了! 果然没错!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学，怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师!还有一个人没到齐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是转学过来坐在圣本旁边\N明明12岁而已却进了我们班...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.73,0:06:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，之前还用国家权力\N随便就...随便就...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.60,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊\N怎么可能会有这种事情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了啦，岩城同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些和岩城同学\N一点关系也没有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么没有关系...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学\N你不是只喜欢年纪大的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也对...不过为什么我会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒一醒啊，老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小学六年级的...我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.94,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学，不可以看旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三年级时的...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我只喜欢年纪大的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这我哪知啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?小友，怎么了啊~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.46,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害羞了吧 这孩子啊\N就是喜欢年纪比他大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...从那时候就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒一醒啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家...人家不再说什么约会了\N所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.56,0:07:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不抱人家，人家也会忍耐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什么也...不做...也不要紧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老...公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小时候的...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险唷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.85,0:08:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦...我是...怎么了...\N好温暖...好柔软的胸膛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁? 你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.06,0:08:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要哭呢?\N喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.87,0:09:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公他...\N他给了人家第一次的温暖...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以人家...才能够在这里活着...\N所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你!求你醒过来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.69,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一点!你不能死!\N快醒过来啊，老公~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉...采...儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了...是莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~~!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采...儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.46,0:10:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了...你醒过来...\N哎呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老...公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你第一次抱人家呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.07,0:10:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了个梦...梦见小时候的我...\N救了你一命...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...不是梦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.35,0:10:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家从那天起，就一直在等待着\N能和老公见面的这一天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿从12岁起就停止了成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.16,0:11:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在那时，因为遇见了你\N所以细胞产生了些微的变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过调查后，我们终于明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿要成为大人\N需要知道什么是‘爱’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而在与你再度相遇之前\N她的细胞仍停留在12岁的模样
